<br />\n<br />\n大嶼山北部穿梭巴士:<br />\nS52,S52A,S56<br />\n<br />\n港鐵巴士:<br />\n港鐵巴士全線暫停服務。"},{"pid":"a0c4f139afd7d644504277e9bdabf0d6e2a47e1e","tid":1713923,"uid":105219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fe24de7544c2939c6a1f0f3da0638406041b5e5f","tid":1713923,"uid":296496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T22:25:22.000Z","msg":"咁係唔係即係一齊搭地鐵呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T22:26:14.000Z","msg":"地鐵會叫你搭返9巴"},{"pid":"2a1964779137fc929225f3b74eddd8084b8fc6e3","tid":1713923,"uid":282280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T22:28:20.000Z","msg":"係唔係巴士司機罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"736dabbabcdf55cc8d2a33810978c524ee1546d4","tid":1713923,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T22:31:13.000Z","msg":"做法不完美，但可接受，要改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解仲可以提供服務"}]}